title: Sneak Attack
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

When the user [[Strike]]s a creature that has the [[Flat-Footed]] condition with an [[Agile]] or [[Finesse]] melee weapon, an agile or finesse unarmed attack,  a ranged weapon attack, __or a ranged unarmed attack__, they also deals the listed [[Precision]] damage. 

For a ranged attack with a thrown weapon, that weapon must also be an agile or finesse weapon.